---
import "../style/global.css";
import handIcon from "../../public/hand.png"
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="short-info-section">
    <div class="short-info-container">
        <h2>Be joyful, be playful!</h2>
        <div class="short-info-content">
            <div class="top-info">
                <Image src={ handIcon } alt="hand icon"/>
                <p>Join the community and open yourself up to others! <br> We are there to help and support each other at any time.</p> </div>
            <div class="middle-info"><p>Relax your body, clear your mind and see what you are <br> truly capable of as you test your own limits.</p> </div>
            <div class="bottom-info"><p>Regardless of your age, abilities, acroyoga is for <br> everybody and will wake up playfulness in everyone.</p> </div>
        </div>
    </div>


</section>